newsitem.title: USA: Marysville BA, Mich., won by First of America.
newsitem.headline: Marysville BA, Mich., won by First of America.

text.p: First of America Securities, Inc said it won $3.2 25 million of Marysville Building Authority, Mich., lease rental 1996 building authority bonds, with a net interest cost of 5.3560 percent.
